parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the key must be jiggled to start the vehicle
the vehicle has difficulty starting
the dashboard lights flicker or go out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The dashboard lights flicker or go out
the headlights and interior lights shut off
the radio and HVAC system shut off
the vehicle loses power while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and stall, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle has difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light is illuminated
the airbag system does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the interior door handles can prevent occupants from exiting the vehicle in an emergency, potentially leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The door handles crack or break
making it impossible to open the door from the inside
the door handles feel loose or floppy
the door handles do not return to their normal position
the door handles stick or jam.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission overheating and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission temperature warning light illuminates
the vehicle loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle is stuck in gear
and there is a burning smell or smoke.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and loss of power can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls
the vehicle loses power
the engine light illuminates
and there is a sudden loss of acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The four-wheel drive system failure can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The "Service Four-Wheel Drive System" warning light illuminates
the vehicle is unable to engage four-wheel drive
and there is a loss of traction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ECM failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine light illuminates
the vehicle loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
and there is a sudden loss of acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ignition switch failure can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
the engine light illuminates
and there is a sudden loss of power.
